{"tid":1275430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警民關係? 仲咁天真 咪引人笑啦","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:26:18.000Z","uid":114328,"like":109,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"da1e34f8a06aa1af60fcb1bd68bb0d57f464c6d0","tid":1275430,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:51:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1274550/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1274550/page/1</a><br />\n<ins>警民關係本身就應該要係咁</ins><br />\n你地係咪忘記哂以前d野<br />\n<br />\n2014年 <br />\n雨傘革命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">87枚催淚彈</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2017/09/%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD-%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-20170926224921_16e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F09%2F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588-20170926224921_16e8.jpg&h=4b36efe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">曹偉雄: <strong>你地冇做錯到</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141002/large/02la4p23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141002%2Flarge%2F02la4p23.jpg&h=6e311471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n七警暗角打人 裹面有<strong>總督察 高級督察 警長 </strong> 拖人去角落做打人 <span style=\"color: red;\">做你地日日所講知法犯法ge野 都只係判兩年</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170218/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170218%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=e2413692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2016年 魚蛋革命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">警員向天開真槍</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/k8jjj.jpg?fit=640%2C360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fk8jjj.jpg%3Ffit%3D640%252C360&h=76f0cdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有果日都被定性為<span style=\"color: red;\">暴亂</span> 結果係咩? 當場有人被人拉 再有人被秋後算帳 坐幾年?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LyXUBEK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyXUBEK.png&h=372dbe8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年 612 <br />\n盧偉聰定性為暴動 <br />\n鎮壓出動無no 速龍 使用布<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">袋彈 橡膠子彈 射頭 150粒催淚彈</span></strong> <br />\n當中幾多人俾胡椒噴到成身痛 拉左現場d義士 再上去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">醫院拉人 </span></strong><br />\n班狗點諗?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係你們嘅榮耀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由果日開始入大學宿舍查搜   見人就抄身分證 搜身 市民人櫂去左邊?<br />\n<br />\n620<br />\n圍又圍過警總  <br />\n濫用救護服務 屈你地唔比救護人員入去 <br />\n救完出黎 有d直頭登記都冇就走左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都算</span></strong></span><br />\n630<br />\n撐警大會 有冇阻止過班人 打記者 打年輕人 非禮 毀壞公物 <br />\n佢地有冇俾人拉啊????????????!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n到今日 7月1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1275077/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1275077/page/1</a><br />\n【鐵証】癲狗開無雙 打退後緊嘅示威者<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/UtzweYa35LB8zRkrNu/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FUtzweYa35LB8zRkrNu%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c566af23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MetroDailyNews/videos/2125184484445328/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMetroDailyNews%2Fvideos%2F2125184484445328%2F&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=e1ccd9c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MetroDailyNews/videos/2125184484445328/</a><br />\n<br />\n12點清場果時 再1粒1粒咁掉催淚彈 掉去記者同人群 <br />\n紅隧Rock block  截紅van無理搜查    旺角捕住你班搭車ge示威者<br />\n<br />\n咁多日<br />\n盧偉聰出黎回應過d乜?<br />\n李家超回應過d乜 ?呃你地話速龍冇位show no<br />\n最重要到而家有冇釋放義士??????<br />\n<br />\n你而家都仲我講緊警民關係?  <br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你有冇諗過比人拉左 比人噴過 比人打 比警察無理搜身d人 ge感受</span></span><br />\n你有冇諗過果位女社工自己一人 同記者係度拖 ge感受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你有你開Po ge自由同發表意見 但一路以黎 事實 話比我地知係無可能  <br />\n但見到咁多正評<br />\n我真係好嬲<br />\n好嬲<br />\n好嬲<br />\n唔好再咁天真啦好嗎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我 屌你老母  </span></span>"},{"pid":"45e00f3fe62a7f4a56c4497582f6121abbfceaea","tid":1275430,"uid":73419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:55:27.000Z","msg":"黎明"},{"pid":"63546cbcd538b281a2df64ea7de09a2d28cfa084","tid":1275430,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:56:38.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"4ee504ad526e062f2251d0228663997afb944b48","tid":1275430,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:57:51.000Z","msg":"同意你<br />\n不過唔好咁嬲啦<br />\n你非常有point<br />\n我相信大家睇得明既"},{"pid":"480791306c5fae4d13ca389c4dc122ca4b8586b7","tid":1275430,"uid":209865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:58:21.000Z","msg":"我勸你唔好阻住人地打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阻人打飛機猶如殺人父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da3918316fa7a3840090f2e71242a5f051aaa90","tid":1275430,"uid":114328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:05:41.000Z","msg":"聽唔到個記者會講乜啊??<br />\n<br />\n關係? <br />\n林鄭同警方都仲係度指責你地<br />\n你地頭先仲係度打飛機 仲咁天真 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對唔對住班死士